FROM THE ROOT:
> hugo server - to run local server
> hugo server --buildDrafts to include blog posts
> hugo - to build to public folder
> hugo version
> hugo help
> hugo new site <website/folder-name>
> hugo new post/<post-name>.md
> hugo server --theme=<theme-folder>

FROM THEMES:
> git clone https://github.com/dim0627/hugo_theme_robust.git

To customize - mirror the folders and files from the theme.
http://localhost:1313/ - to access local website

EXTRA:
https://gohugo.io/overview/introduction/ - docs
https://themes.gohugo.io/ - hugo themes
https://georgecushen.com/create-your-website-with-hugo/ - deployment
http://convertico.com/ - convert png to ico

GIT:
https://georgecushen.com/create-your-website-with-hugo/ - Getting started with Github

git add .
git commit -m "Commit name"
git push -u origin master

hugo
cd public
git add .
git commit -m "Build website"
git push -u origin master
